verbose_text: However, only few of thymocytes in tnpo3 mutants express rag1 (XREF_FIG B and 5C), despite normal expression levels of a thymocyte marker, ccr9b (XREF_FIG B), suggesting that intrathymic defects contribute to impaired T cell development in tnpo3 deficient fish.
